org.dmfs.android.calendarcontent.provider

Class CalendarContentContract.ContentItem

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.dmfs.android.calendarcontent.provider.CalendarContentContract.ContentItem
  • Enclosing class:
    CalendarContentContract

    public static final class CalendarContentContract.ContentItem
extends java.lang.Object
    Represents a list of all items provided by the API. This list is completely read-only - you can not modify any of these values.

    There exist two kinds of items in this table: Page items and calendar items. Page items contain sections (at least one) and sections can contain pages and calendars.

    The basic structure of the items is as follows:
